sentence: Our principal executive and financial officers have reviewed the effectiveness of our `` disclosure controls and procedures '' (as defined in the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 Rules 13a-14 (c) and 15d-14 (c)) within the end of the period covered by this Annual Report on Form 10-K and have concluded that the disclosure controls and procedures are not effective due to a material weakness to ensure that material information relating to the Company is recorded, processed, summarized, and reported in a timely manner.
